T1  - Nonparametric Analysis of Random Utility Models
AU  - Kitamura, Yuichi
AU  - Stoye, Jörg
Y1  - 2018/11/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA14478
